WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.548 --> 00:00:01.714
Good morning, family.

00:00:01.714 --> 00:00:05.913
I have another video for you all.

00:00:07.309 --> 00:00:09.520
I have some things I want to say.

00:00:21.462 --> 00:00:21.697
I'm a watchman, and the Lord shows me a lot of things.

00:00:21.697 --> 00:00:26.804
A lot of things he shows me are very heavy.

00:00:26.804 --> 00:00:35.514
He gives this stuff to me when I'm praying and says, 'Hey, Brandon, heads up.

00:00:35.514 --> 00:00:40.106
This is what's coming down the road here.

00:00:40.106 --> 00:00:50.348
' There are some things we can avoid and some things we can't.

00:00:50.348 --> 00:00:56.093
Like I said, I'm always trying to figure out...

00:01:05.400 --> 00:01:05.743
I know we have power and authority as believers.

00:01:05.743 --> 00:01:20.920
We're seated with Him in the heavenlies, and I know that when we join together as a group and we pray, I tell you all the plan of the enemy.

00:01:20.920 --> 00:01:25.428
I'm blowing my trumpet.

00:01:25.428 --> 00:01:33.980
I'm a watchman on the wall saying, 'Listen, the bozo devil is going to try to do this.

00:01:33.980 --> 00:01:36.508
Let's stop it.

00:01:36.508 --> 00:01:47.799
' I know the Lord's trying to warn you all, warn the world, and warn America.

00:01:50.866 --> 00:01:57.714
I thought this was interesting: he made a statement to me while I was out taking care of my dogs.

00:02:08.564 --> 00:02:19.646
He said, 'Brandon, if Abraham's intercession for Sodom and Gomorrah—when he was praying, he said, Lord, if there be ten righteous, would you spare the city?

00:02:22.569 --> 00:02:35.898
And he said back to Abraham, Yes, I'd be willing to spare the city for ten righteous.

00:02:35.898 --> 00:02:47.417
' I believe if he would have taken it down a step further...

00:02:47.417 --> 00:03:02.240
because I know he thought in his mind there has to be ten righteous people standing in behalf of Sodom and Gomorrah.

00:03:02.240 --> 00:03:12.545
They were a very immoral city, of course, and it was wiped off the face of the earth.

00:03:12.687 --> 00:03:26.585
He was interceding for them and he said, 'Brandon, if I was willing to do that for them back then under the Old Covenant without Jesus, how much more with you interceding now would I do it for you?

00:03:26.585 --> 00:03:38.120
' He said, 'I called you on YouTube to tell my people what's coming, not for a lot of it to come.

00:03:38.120 --> 00:03:48.951
' I believe with our group of intercessory prayer people, we are able to do a lot of damage to the kingdom of darkness.

00:03:55.994 --> 00:04:00.337
I warned you all about the water attack, about the men trying to pour stuff into the lakes and mess with our water.

00:04:00.337 --> 00:04:04.428
I believe we can stop that.

00:04:04.428 --> 00:04:16.199
Whenever he came to me and said that, it was just out of the clear blue.

00:04:24.669 --> 00:04:34.660
I was cleaning up dog feces, doing my normal thing with my puppies, and when he said that to me, I was like, 'Wow, Lord, where does this come from?

00:04:34.660 --> 00:04:53.000
' I wasn't even really praying; I'm always in the state of prayer in my heart, always just talking and having communion with the Father.

00:04:53.320 --> 00:05:00.306
He knows I'm always willing to jump in that river and pray with Him.

00:05:00.306 --> 00:05:02.119
It is always a flow.

00:05:02.299 --> 00:05:12.119
The more you build that, the more you'll flow with the Holy Spirit.

00:05:12.119 --> 00:05:19.626
This was not a real supernatural moment; it was just a normal day, spraying off the grass and cleaning up the yard, and he just said that to me.

00:05:19.626 --> 00:05:21.373
It hit me hard.

00:05:33.240 --> 00:05:34.760
He said, 'Remember, Brandon: If My people who are called by My name would humble themselves and pray and turn from their wicked ways...

00:05:34.760 --> 00:05:50.667
' Then he stopped and said to me, 'I did not say if the world would humble themselves and pray.

00:05:50.667 --> 00:05:54.169
I didn't say the world.

00:05:54.169 --> 00:05:56.730
I didn't say Joe Biden.

00:05:56.730 --> 00:06:00.200
I didn't say Nancy Pelosi.

00:06:00.200 --> 00:06:02.560
I said, My people.

00:06:02.560 --> 00:06:15.065
' He's talking about you and me, people who are on fire for Him.

00:06:15.065 --> 00:06:25.324
If we would humble ourselves and pray, we would hear from heaven and He would heal our land.

00:06:26.351 --> 00:06:40.938
He would deliver us from what's going on and do what needs to be done to help turn around the nation.

00:06:40.938 --> 00:07:06.493
If we have a group of people—maybe I have a 10,000-strong group of believers on here worldwide—I know we can do something big.

00:07:06.493 --> 00:07:18.168
Some of my prayer videos get a couple thousand people who watch the whole thing.

00:07:18.168 --> 00:07:23.759
I know you're interceding with me the whole time.

00:07:23.759 --> 00:07:32.651
I just want to encourage you all that this is not a 'sky is falling' time.

00:07:38.271 --> 00:07:45.560
I told you all when I went to the throne, he said to me, 'Brandon, I never designed the armor for retreat.

00:07:45.560 --> 00:08:01.390
I designed the armor to take dominion and authority, and take back what the devil's tried to steal.

00:08:01.390 --> 00:08:18.900
' It's marching forward, taking action, taking that sword of the spirit, the shield of faith, and the helmet of salvation and smacking that devil in the head.

00:08:18.900 --> 00:08:24.800
It's not to run away because there's no armor for the backside.

00:08:28.445 --> 00:08:34.039
The Lord said this to me: 'Brandon, the devil is the Lord of the Flies.

00:08:37.468 --> 00:08:37.742
He is like a fly.

00:08:37.742 --> 00:08:42.394
' That's how the Lord showed me.

00:08:42.394 --> 00:08:51.664
He said, 'Do you know how you get the devil not to bother you so much?

00:08:51.664 --> 00:08:54.550
' I said, 'How, Lord?

00:08:54.550 --> 00:08:59.959
' He said, 'Get hot.

00:08:59.959 --> 00:09:02.399
Get extremely on fire for Me.

00:09:02.399 --> 00:09:10.675
For a fly does not land on a flame or a very hot surface.

00:09:10.675 --> 00:09:16.729
' He said the hotter you get with Me, the less a fly can land.

00:09:16.729 --> 00:09:25.075
He said they land on the lukewarm when they smell food or they smell poo.

00:09:25.075 --> 00:09:31.734
Flies do, but they will not land on something that's on fire.

00:09:31.734 --> 00:09:57.290
He said the devil is like a fly, and the more you become on fire for Me, the less that devil's going to try to mess with you because he's a fly and he doesn't want to touch a hot surface because he'll get burnt.

00:09:57.290 --> 00:10:03.040
That's what I'm trying to tell you all.

00:10:03.040 --> 00:10:05.871
Get on fire for Jesus.

00:10:05.871 --> 00:10:09.276
How do you get on fire?

00:10:09.276 --> 00:10:12.151
Spend time with Him daily.

00:10:12.151 --> 00:10:18.667
Get before Him, get on your knees, and worship the Father.

00:10:18.667 --> 00:10:24.749
Read His Bible, pray, spend time with Him in worship.

00:10:24.749 --> 00:10:30.752
Worship Him in singing and in praying, and you'll get on fire for Jesus.

00:10:30.752 --> 00:10:37.880
Faith comes by hearing and hearing by the word of God.

00:10:37.880 --> 00:10:42.091
Get that word down inside of you.

00:10:42.091 --> 00:10:49.439
I'm telling you, that fire is going to be like a furnace.

00:10:49.439 --> 00:10:58.211
You keep putting coals and gas in it, and that devil's going to run.

00:10:58.211 --> 00:11:02.570
He doesn't want to get around that fire.

00:11:02.570 --> 00:11:11.026
He'll be like that little fly: you touch the flame, you burn him up.

00:11:11.026 --> 00:11:16.536
That's the way the Lord showed me.

00:11:18.200 --> 00:11:25.100
I started dealing with stuff and he goes, 'Brandon, you're getting lukewarm.

00:11:25.100 --> 00:11:35.730
Son, you've got to come back under that fire and fan that flame.

00:11:35.730 --> 00:11:45.608
' I heard somebody preaching this last Wednesday about authority in your realm of authority.

00:11:46.124 --> 00:11:49.987
I believe we have power and authority over storms.

00:11:53.635 --> 00:11:54.010
I take it all the time.

00:11:54.010 --> 00:12:06.100
We pray over our storms, we take communion, we tell the storm to die like Jesus did: 'Peace, be still.

00:12:06.100 --> 00:12:14.780
' You can call the storm; you're not going to hail on my property.

00:12:16.903 --> 00:12:28.880
You're not going to have strong winds; we're not going to lose power; we're not going to have any damage to our houses or trees.

00:12:28.880 --> 00:12:39.756
Satan, I bind you and I tell you now, you get out of here and you leave my stuff alone.

00:12:39.756 --> 00:12:47.199
We have authority over you and we have authority over the weather.

00:12:47.199 --> 00:12:59.937
I command this weather to be peace and be still over my area in the name of Jesus.

00:12:59.937 --> 00:13:03.079
I command any tornadoes to go away now.

00:13:03.079 --> 00:13:05.489
Go back up in that cloud and stop it.

00:13:05.489 --> 00:13:10.943
That's just the way we talk to them.

00:13:10.943 --> 00:13:17.982
My mom, my dad, my wife—we all talk to the storms.

00:13:25.240 --> 00:13:26.360
That's how we believe and operate in the realm of the spirit.

00:13:27.120 --> 00:13:29.039
We take authority over the storms.

00:13:30.439 --> 00:13:36.396
I had a lady asking for rain for a certain area in Texas where they didn't have any.

00:13:36.396 --> 00:13:42.250
I told her I'd stand with her for rain.

00:13:42.250 --> 00:13:53.035
She emailed back with a picture showing all the rain like a river.

00:13:53.035 --> 00:13:56.800
I did what I said I'd do.

00:13:56.800 --> 00:14:00.720
I started speaking the rain.

00:14:00.720 --> 00:14:11.920
I told it to come forth over Houston, interceding for Houston and The Woodlands, Texas.

00:14:11.920 --> 00:14:20.920
I started speaking to that rain, and now they have rivers and moats of rain everywhere.

00:14:20.920 --> 00:14:33.315
Not only can we stop the rain, but we can cause the rain to come forth because we have authority over it.

00:14:33.315 --> 00:14:38.388
I call rain in all the time.

00:14:38.388 --> 00:14:55.979
It starts getting dry and they say, 'The drought monitor is getting bad again and there's going to be no rain; lakes are drying up.

00:14:55.979 --> 00:14:57.540
' No.

00:14:57.540 --> 00:15:04.540
Rain, I call you forth in the name of Jesus.

00:15:23.102 --> 00:15:23.506
I say, 'Rain, come from the north, south, east, and west.

00:15:25.040 --> 00:15:28.340
You will not have drought over this area.

00:15:28.340 --> 00:15:31.720
' I call that rain in.

00:15:31.720 --> 00:15:33.777
Rain, come forth.

00:15:43.360 --> 00:15:45.039
I speak low-pressure systems to come in for the Gulf moisture to come up, or wherever the jet stream comes over.

00:15:53.556 --> 00:15:53.800
I call forth four inches of rain over the next week or two.

00:15:55.263 --> 00:16:11.314
I thank you, Father, that You're the Lord of the harvest and You will bring rain for my crops, the trees, and the grass.

00:16:11.314 --> 00:16:20.790
You have to use your authority in these last days more than ever before.

00:16:20.790 --> 00:16:34.449
When you hear the weatherman say there's a storm coming, you say, 'Not my house, not my area, not where I tread.

00:16:34.449 --> 00:16:45.529
' You've got to learn how to be bold about it, not shrinking back saying, 'He won't protect me.

00:16:45.529 --> 00:16:52.548
' No, He's a good God; He's no respecter of persons.

00:16:58.380 --> 00:16:58.690
You have power and authority over the weather and your city.

00:17:03.355 --> 00:17:03.639
You pray over the city for your police officers and churches.

00:17:04.930 --> 00:17:06.320
The authority of the believer works.

00:17:06.320 --> 00:17:19.674
At the name of Jesus, every knee will bow and every tongue will confess that He is Lord.

00:17:19.674 --> 00:17:26.799
That's the kind of power we have in Him.

00:17:26.799 --> 00:17:33.500
If there be ten righteous, He'd spare the city.

00:17:33.500 --> 00:17:48.234
How much more would He be willing to spare America or delay things to allow the harvest of souls?

00:17:48.234 --> 00:17:52.629
Why has He not come back yet?

00:17:52.629 --> 00:18:00.463
Because He is a God of mercy and He wants more harvest.

00:18:00.463 --> 00:18:03.200
He sent His only begotten son to die for you.

00:18:03.200 --> 00:18:09.746
He doesn't want anybody to perish, but for all to come to repentance.

00:18:09.746 --> 00:18:12.599
Why hasn't the Rapture happened?

00:18:12.599 --> 00:18:21.250
Because He's looking for the harvest that matters most to Him.

00:18:21.250 --> 00:18:25.210
Gold, diamonds, and jewels—that's what He uses for pavement.

00:18:25.210 --> 00:18:29.926
He doesn't care about gold; it's asphalt to Him.

00:18:29.926 --> 00:18:35.302
What's important to Him is the heart of a man.

00:18:35.302 --> 00:18:40.850
It's important to Him that your loved ones are saved.

00:18:45.053 --> 00:18:54.520
I want to encourage you all to believe God for the big things: speak to your mountains, speak to the storms, speak to your finances.

00:18:54.520 --> 00:19:04.860
Believe for the impossible, because all things are possible to him who believes.

00:19:04.860 --> 00:19:10.480
Father, I thank You for every single person here.

00:19:10.480 --> 00:19:13.535
We have a mighty moving army.

00:19:13.535 --> 00:19:20.830
We thank You that we have authority over storms and rain.

00:19:20.830 --> 00:19:26.560
We call forth an abundant harvest of rain over drought areas.

00:19:26.560 --> 00:19:36.651
We call forth finances and thank You that You supply all our needs according to Your riches in glory.

00:19:36.651 --> 00:19:39.954
We call people healed.

00:19:39.954 --> 00:19:53.822
Jesus, You took it all on the cross for us so we don't have to be sick.

00:19:53.822 --> 00:19:57.669
We call our bodies well and whole.

00:19:57.669 --> 00:19:59.300
We call marriages restored.

00:19:59.300 --> 00:20:10.060
Speak to your marriage: 'My marriage is good; my marriage is awesome and full of love and joy.

00:20:10.060 --> 00:20:17.590
' We will not have a divorce or corruption in this house.

00:20:32.257 --> 00:20:32.733
We bless our children that they'll be prosperous and not struggle.

00:20:46.056 --> 00:20:46.434
Thank You, Lord, that You raise them up.

00:20:46.434 --> 00:20:51.679
It's part of my covenant rights to have children that worship You.

00:20:51.679 --> 00:20:56.747
If my children go wayward, You'll bring them back.

00:20:56.747 --> 00:21:01.525
You'll leave the ninety-nine to go after the one.

00:21:03.240 --> 00:21:05.347
You have power and authority.

00:21:05.347 --> 00:21:06.400
Read Ephesians over and over again and get that word deep inside of you.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.600
If you say you don't hear God, He is speaking all the time through the Bible.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
Pick it up and read it.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
His mercies are new every morning.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
I hope this video blessed you.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
Know that you have that authority.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
The devil has no authority to torment you.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
You tell him, 'Thus far and no further.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
' You've got to talk to him like a dog because he's a dog.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
God is good and He's faithful.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
Jesus loves you, and we love you.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
Have a blessed day.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
Bye-bye.
